  <brief_title>Study of Histological Findings of the Internal Inguinal Ring in Patients With Indirect Inguinal Hernia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Histological Findings of the Internal Inguinal Ring in Patients With Indirect Inguinal Hernia</official_title>
