  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The histology of the internal inguinal ring in patients with indirect hernia submitted to
      elective surgery was studied. In contrast with recently published studies, the investigators
      believe that histological findings of the internal inguinal ring would reflect those
      associated and expected with normal aging.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
